channel.title: Imputing Item ID's
channel.description:
OK, ive read quite a few threads and havent found an answer for this question. I go to help and Item List and see all the different items and there id's, but the command only takes 3 digits and most of the items have 4 digit Id's. Can anyone tell me how to fix this/what im doing wrong?
Any help would be much appreciated and im sure this has been answered before and apologize that i couldnt find the posts.
Thank You for you time,
~Wuzzin~

item.dc:creator: @mythicfire mythicfire
item.description:
@mythicfire wrote:

the command takes up 4 digits. If it is a 3 digit item, you put a zero in front of it.
